2. Modifications by the EZ-FLASH Air Kernel KO project
------------------------------------------------------
Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0. Modified areas include:
  - UTF-8 text renderer and font-block lookup (source/draw.c)
  - Korean string table and three-language plumbing
    (source/lang.c, source/lang.h, source/ezkernelnew.c, source/setwindow.c)
  - Hangul SD filename support: FatFs CP949 codepage + UTF-8 LFN
    (source/ff16)
  - Generated font headers (source/font_kor.h, source/font_cjk.h)
  - Kernel slimming: FPGA bitstream deduplicated against image.bin at
    0x08195000, gated by a CRC32 check
  - Build tooling (build.sh, tools/link_kernel.py)

